1. *Njegovo* ćudoređe je bilo poznato u celoj zajednici. (His fairness was known throughout the community.)
2. Ono što je uradio *njegovo* dete bilo je neprihvatljivo. (What his child did was unacceptable.)
3. *Njegov*a je žena bila veoma lepa. (His wife was very beautiful.)
4. *Njegove* su knjige bile veoma popularne. (His books were very popular.)
5. *Njegovoj* sestri je bilo veoma teško da se pomiri sa situacijom. (It was very difficult for his sister to come to terms with the situation.)